`package.json`, `.env.example`, `.gitignore`, `README.md`, `public/styles.css`, and under `src/`: `server.js`, `app.js`, `db.js`, `seed.js`, `middleware/{auth,csrf}.js`, `routes/{auth,patient,doctor,reception}.js`, plus EJS views in `src/views/`.

